dc_title_s: Deed William J. Wheeler and others to Anna Margaret Reid
dc_description_s: This 2 page deed includes details about the conveyance of two tracts of land near Barnegat Inlet. The deed is stapled to an accompanying map which illustrates the tracts of land conveyed by the deed.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|This deed was recorded in Book 504, Page 17 of Deeds of Ocean County.
